points. Also state the main topic in one or two words. If the essay is argumentative,
classify its stance on the main topic as "pro" or "con" or "neutral" if the article
is not argumentative.

Answer in structured JSON format (without Markdown formatting) like so:
{
    "key_points": ["key point 1", "key point 2", ...],
    "main_topic": "article topic",
    "stance": "stance on topic as pro, con, or neutral"
}
